data.description: This beautiful two-story home offers 4 bedrooms/3 bathrooms. A large master bedroom is located upstairs on one side of the hall. The other two bedrooms are good-sized, with a full-sized bathroom down the hall. There is one bedroom conveniently located downstairs and near to the downstairs bath. The living room/dining room combo is spacious and enhanced with a curved staircase. The kitchen is spacious, with tile countertops and a large walk-in pantry. The kitchen opens to the family room, highlighted with a modern fireplace. The laundry room is located downstairs. Huge backyard with a cove patio, a water softener to the entire house.  A must-see!
